# This file documents the revision history
# for DBIx::Class::Storage::Statistics::SimpleTable

0.02
  - First non-dev release
  - Support customized headers
  - Support a threshold for query durations that are to be logged
  - Added report_row_count accessor to the numer of queries actually logged
  - Support skipping of parameter column
  - Allow simple chaining of SimpleTable statistic gatherers
    (that is: ->report now does its best to DWIM)

0.01_01 - Tue Mar  3 04:14:26 2009
  Initial release

